Barring last minute change, Oyo State Government has modified the resumption of schools slated for June 29. According to the new arrangement, only teachers are to resume on June 29th while students in terminal classes resume a week later. The Government had earlier directed all terminal classes including Primary Six (Pry 6), Junior Secondary School Three (JSS3) and Senior Secondary School Three (SSS3) to resume on June 29 ahead of preparations for their various exams. Top government source hinted that the change in plans became imperative in view of a latest expert report which indicated the non-readiness of schools in terms of meeting the various government protocols. Details shortlyâ€¦